      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard. It has successfully undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Offering a refined driving experience and a well-preserved interior, this model represents a premier choice for those seeking a balance of performance and long-term value. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate this vehicle's superior condition in person.",
