    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable car without the brand-new price tag. Everything runs smoothly, and it\u2019s just waiting for someone to take it on its next big road trip! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive. Can't wait to hear from you!",
      "price": 34500.0,
