      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car and it's been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it still runs like a dream and is ready for its next big adventure. You might find a few tiny signs of character from its time on the road, but overall it\u2019s a fantastic, comfy ride that\u2019s been looked after properly. I'd love for you to come by, check it out, and take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 31500.0,
